#include 'template.wml'

<table class="mydemo">
<tr class="mydemo">
<td class="mydemo">

<h3>Demo</h3>

<ol>
<li>
Generate an image with <menupath>&lt;Toolbox&gt; -&gt; Xtns -&gt; Script-Fu -&gt; Patterns -&gt; "3D Truchet"</menupath>.
</li>
<li>
Duplicate the layer using <menupath>&lt;Layers&gt; -&gt; Duplicate Layer</menupath>.
</li>
<li>
Render a nice gradient on the lower layer.
</li>
<li>
Generate an alpha on the upper layer by using <menupath>&lt;Layers&gt; -&gt; "Add Layer Mask..."</menupath>.
</li>
<li>
Select the paintbrush tool and paint black strokes on the alpha
of the upper layer.
</li>
<li>
Switch to a grey colour and paint grey strokes.
</li>
<li>
Finalize the Layer's Mask using <menupath>&lt;Layers&gt; -&gt; "Apply Layer Mask"</menupath>
</li>
</ol>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
